title: Antiloop - LP & Fastline People
description:
Two albums from the Swedish dance/trance group Antiloop, LP (1997) and Fastline People (2000).

The MP3 version of LP already here misses track 6, Analogue Relaxation. This version is encoded from the FLAC-files available here, using Lame 3.97 VBR, command-line settings -V2 --vbr-new, generally accepted as resulting in files hardly possible to differate from lossless for most people. The lame header is:

Quality                       : 77
Version String                : Lame 3.97
Tag Revision                  : 0
VBR Method                    : vbr-mtrh
Lowpass Filter                : 18600
Psycho-acoustic Model         : nspsytune
Safe Joint Stereo             : yes
nogap (continued)             : no
nogap (continuation)          : no
ATH Type                      : 4
ABR Bitrate                   : 32
Noise Shaping                 : 1
Stereo Mode                   : Joint Stereo
Unwise Settings Used          : no
Input Frequency               : 44.1kHz

Fastline People is not as good as LP, but still enjoyable. It was not available here, but I found a good copy elsewhere. It is encoded with Lame 4.0alpha!!! (I think that anything but released versions should only be used for true testing and not be sread, but it is the best available version) with the following Lame header:

Quality                       : 75
Version String                : Lame 4.0a
Tag Revision                  : 0
VBR Method                    : vbr-new / vbr-mt
Lowpass Filter                : 19600
Psycho-acoustic Model         : nspsytune
Safe Joint Stereo             : no
nogap (continued)             : no
nogap (continuation)          : no
ATH Type                      : 0
ABR Bitrate                   : 193
Noise Shaping                 : 1
Stereo Mode                   : Joint Stereo
Unwise Settings Used          : no
Input Frequency               : 44.1kHz


Enjoy and leave a comment if you want to.
